Package apryraz.eworld

This package contains an implementation of the Envelope World, where an agent has to find the location of the envelopes using the detector sensor to get information about the world.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AMessage
    Class for representing messages exchanged between agents and the World interface object
    EFState  
    EnvelopeFinder
    This agent performs a sequence of movements, and after each movement it "senses" from the evironment the resulting position and then the outcome from the smell sensor, to try to locate the position of Envelope
